But beware, I have seen Made In Germany on parts that were shipped to 
Mexico for assembly with other parts made who knows where. Made in 
Germany parts can sometimes be had riveted to other parts by worn out 
machines inspected by Hay-sus.

The Henco en Mexico stickers sometimes fall off.
